    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v1
    v2 = (0.87 / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.95) - (v1 + 0.45 - v2 + 0.47)))
    v1 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.78 + tmp + 0.17) * (tmp + 0.04 + v2 + 0.57)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.sin(tmp + 0.36) - tmp))
